<bibRefCitation author="Li, L. F. &amp; Rasnitsyn, A. P. &amp; Shih, C. K. &amp; Labandeira, C. C. &amp; Buffington, M. &amp; Li, D. Q. &amp; Ren, D." pageId="1" pageNumber="270" pagination="810 - 842" refId="ref4084" refString="Li, L. F., Rasnitsyn, A. P., Shih, C. K., Labandeira, C. C., Buffington, M., Li, D. Q. &amp; Ren, D. (2018) Phylogeny of Evanioidea (Hymenoptera, Apocrita), with descriptions of new Mesozoic species from China and Myanmar. Systematic Entomology, 43, 810 - 842. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / syen. 12315" type="journal article" year="2018">
Li 
